titles.title: A resolution honoring the life of Nebraska community leader John Edmund Gottschalk.
A resolution honoring the life of Nebraska community leader John Edmund Gottschalk.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent.

bill.summary: This resolution honors the life and legacy of John Edmund Gottschalk for his unwavering dedication to Nebraska as a civic leader and philanthropist.
